Leading Nollywood actor, Kanayo O. Kanayo, has refuted claims that sex-for-roles exist in the Nigerian movie industry. The actor on his Instagram page urged Nigerians to pay no attention to people with such opinions about the industry. He stated that it was a shame that many girls in the industry are not working hard enough. He wrote, “When you hear of sex-for-roles in Nollywood, please do not believe all you are told. “Many of the girls are not working hard to live up to the roles they are cast for. Quite a shame.”